videos.description: Myles Powell drives into the paint and Omari Spellman swats it away.
videos.headline: Villanova 's Spellman denies lay-in attempt

videos.description: Myles Powell connects with Myles Cale who drains the three.
videos.headline: Pirates' Cale drains wide-open triple

videos.description: Seton Hall's Myles Powell gets out in transition and swishes in a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Myles Powell in transition, drains great triple.

videos.description: Myles Powell runs in transition and hits a 3-pointer from the top of the arc.
videos.headline: Pirates' Powell is on fire and drains another deep three

videos.description: Myles Cale with the great hustle to keep the ball in-bounds, throws it to Khadeen Carrington who drives it home for a great lay-up.
videos.headline: Pirates' Carrington soars through the air for lay-in

videos.description: Khadeen Carrington gets fouled on play, and drains one of two free throws making it a tied game at 52-52.
videos.headline: Carrington makes it a tie game with a and one

videos.description: Myles Cale slams it home, and gets carried off the court because his leg cramped up.
videos.headline: Pirates' Cale makes clutch dunk

videos.description: Jalen Brunson pushes through the defense and gets the layup for Villanova.
videos.headline: Wildcats' Brunson drives into the paint for lay-in

videos.description: Jalen Brunson hits the jumper that gives Villanova the lead.
videos.headline: Villanova's Brunson hits clutch jumper
